properties.areaDesc: Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 8 at 3:46AM EST until January 8 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and waves 2
to 4 feet.

* WHERE...Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST THIS EVENING
